column5: Hi all,  When i went to bed last night the lake was liquid........when i woke up this morning it looked like this............................   <iframe width="420" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/jIn4kGLUJts" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>      Next weekend should see my first holes drilled   :thumbsup_anim:
JEALOUS! -11 is the forecasted low for here tonight.

I hope you catch nothing...and your gas auger won't work...and you fall through a couple of times and lose some gear. Did I just type that outloud  You lucky bugger. Give em hell next weekend Simon and do share it with us. I'm hoping for ice by Dec 17-18 weekend. So until then I will be green with envy.
Only 5-6 short weeks til I see that!!! Damn, I hate waiting. Thanks for the pics!
4 more short months and I can take the boat back out !!!! COME ON SPRINGTIME!!!!!!
Hahaha, that's hilarious Simon.  Can't wait myself
Dood... get with the program Guess will have to watch your reports until the south gets ice over Just got 11Lbs of pure goodness for the freezer.... I think I can survive on that til ice
I want to cry I'm so jealous
Limey, all I can say is Reports Reports Reports!!  Good luck next weekend you lucky bugger!  Rob C
